{"id": "1412718678549598219", "channel_id": "1412718678549598219", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**小编在弥萨格大学听到一条传言：**\n在大学后院的某处空地，曾有一个抱着画具的人追着守密人跑了一整晚，他嘴里嚷嚷着：“为我画一幅肖像画吧！为我画一幅肖像画吧！”\n气喘吁吁的守密人被那人扑倒在地，耳边再次响起魔音：“为我~画一幅~肖像画吧~”\n\n据说自那夜后，守密人便“染”上了画画的爱好。\n👄：守密人，夜晚将至。画笔与画布已备好，为皮克曼画一幅肖像画吧~\n——————————————\n**注：**此传说过于久远，真实性已无从考证，小编对传播此事带来的后果概不负责👋\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n**The editor heard a rumor at Mythag University:**\nSomewhere in an open space in the university courtyard, there was a person carrying painting supplies who chased the Keeper all night long, shouting, \"Paint a portrait for me! Paint a portrait for me!\"\nThe out-of-breath Keeper was knocked to the ground by that person, and the enchanting voice echoed in his ears again: \"Draw a portrait for me~\"\n\nIt is said that since that night, the Keeper has \"caught\" a passion for painting.\n👄: Keeper, night is approaching. The brush and canvas are ready, let's paint a portrait for Pickman~\n——————————————\n**Note: **This legend is too ancient to verify its authenticity, and the editor takes no responsibility for the consequences of spreading this matter.👋", "timestamp": "2025-09-03T08:39:40.010000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-03T08:45:58.117000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🧑‍🎨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 29}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1412718678985801738", "filename": "-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 895912, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1412718678549598219/1412718678985801738/-.jpg?ex=69ccd9cc&is=69cb884c&hm=afacb41a3d3d9e82f170a5650a0aafa10127e5dbc5d9f2187482aa5077a9fe68&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412718678549598219", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.2 额外放送：弥萨格大学传说一则┊Extra Broadcast: A Legend of Mythag University", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "t